---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'July 20, 2026';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service - Savelle Design"
  description="The terms that govern use of savelledesign.com and the services offered."
>
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-4">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 mb-12">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

      <div class="prose prose-lg prose-zinc max-w-none
        prose-headings:font-bold prose-headings:text-zinc-900
        prose-h2:text-2xl prose-h2:mt-10 prose-h2:mb-4
        prose-p:text-zinc-600 prose-p:leading-relaxed
        prose-strong:text-zinc-900 prose-strong:font-semibold
        prose-ul:text-zinc-600
        prose-a:text-zinc-900 prose-a:no-underline hover:prose-a:text-zinc-600">
        <p>
          These terms govern your use of savelledesign.com and any design or development services
          you engage from Savelle McThias / Savelle Design (&ldquo;I&rdquo; or &ldquo;me&rdquo;).
          By using the site or engaging a project, you agree to these terms.
        </p>

        <h2>Services</h2>
        <p>I provide UX/UI design, web development, branding, email campaign design, and related
          consulting. Specific scope, deliverables, timelines, and fees are agreed in a proposal
          before work begins.</p>

        <h2>Engagements and payment</h2>
        <p>Project engagements are billed according to the terms in their individual proposal or
          agreement. Payment schedules, milestones, and invoicing details are confirmed with you
          before work starts.</p>

        <h2>Intellectual property</h2>
        <p>Deliverables I create for you become yours upon full payment, except for any third-party
          assets and my own pre-existing tools, templates, and methods. The content, design, and
          code of this website remain my property and may not be copied without permission.</p>

        <h2>Acceptable use</h2>
        <p>You agree not to misuse the site&mdash;no attempts to disrupt it, access it unlawfully,
          or use it to infringe others&apos; rights.</p>

        <h2>Disclaimer and limitation of liability</h2>
        <p>The site and its content are provided &ldquo;as is&rdquo; without warranties of any kind.
          To the fullest extent permitted by law, my liability for any claim relating to the site or
          a service is limited to the amount you paid for that service.</p>

        <h2>Governing law</h2>
        <p>These terms are governed by the laws of the State of Arizona, without regard to its
          conflict-of-law rules.</p>

        <h2>Changes</h2>
        <p>I may update these terms from time to time. Continued use of the site after an update
          means you accept the revised terms.</p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>Questions about these terms? Email
          <a href="mailto:savellem@gmail.com">savellem@gmail.com</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
